title: Piggy (Ghosts) [live/lossless/edited]
description:
i was having a hard time finding a good version of this song to go in a compilation that i am making so i put this together. i took the Minneapolis MN 11/25/2008 recording; tweaked the volume a bit and filtered it some.

it was converted a couple times, all through lossless formats.

im uploading this just to share. if you dont like it, i dont really give a shit. if you do then hooray.

format is Apple Lossless. enjoy.
